HEADWORD: Conversazione
<hw>Con`ver*sa`zi*o"ne</hw> <pr>(? ⟦or⟧ ?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>;
<plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>Conversazioni</plw> <pr>(#)</pr></plu>. <ety>[It.
